Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:47.42,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:53.01,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Nase!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you haven't been going to your\Nmatches? Waya was worried that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:14.94,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(340,115)}The Sixty-Eighth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:14.95,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx330\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Forfeits
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.29,0:02:24.96,Background,,0,0,0,,He's going to quit being a pro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that he would quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from his teacher that he became\Na pro by passing a very difficult test...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Shindou-kun say he was going to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, but he hasn't gone to any of his matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to two of them in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But even though we've received\Nmatch schedules in the mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:09.04,Background,,0,0,0,,he hasn't gone to one since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He took a break immediately\Nafter Golden Week didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he had to go to Hiroshima\Nfor something Go related.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a match then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't had an absence since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that he has been absent\Nfrom his matches to come to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't know very\Nmuch about the Go world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so it didn't bother me that Shindou-kun\Ncame to school every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't tell me anything even when I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He suddenly changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:04:00.59,Background,,0,0,0,,He used to be so cheery that it was annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he has his reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He did become a pro, he's made\Nhimself a path in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.77,0:04:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So both my husband and I have decided\Nto just watch over him for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:17.78,Background,,0,0,0,,but I just can't help but be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look into it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:28.59,Background,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you explain this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Weekly Go? Where did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,From Koike-kun. But more importantly,\Nexplain this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They list the records for all the pros in the scores\Nsection, but yours is filled with forfeits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm not playing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Weren't you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you weren't going to play\Nwith me anymore because I suck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you mean you're\Nnot going to play anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to quit being a pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:13.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If Sai doesn't come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe. I might quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:20.80,Background,,0,0,0,,What a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.09,Background,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but you quit the Go club to become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hikaru... What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably need to study for\Nhigh school entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari, stay after school and study with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki doesn't have time! We\Nhave a tournament coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tournament, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by 'Tournament, huh?'!\NDon't you dare look down on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were much more passionate when\Nyou were striving to beat Kaiou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be in this next tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Natsume, Koike, and I, the three of us,\Nwe're going to challenge Kaiou again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Mitani-kun, you're going to be in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to go!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou, are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're never going to let you\Nback in again, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki! Leave him alone. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitani-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.75,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was absorbed in Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:35.63,Memory,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work hard here in the Go club\Nwith Tsutsui-san. Right, Tsutsui-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.42,Memory,,0,0,0,,Tsutsui-san! I brought Mitani!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:49.14,Memory,,0,0,0,,It's a team tournament, three people\Nper team. We win if two of us win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.27,Memory,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:52.48,Memory,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,For the tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:03.32,Memory,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sai. I can't tell unless I play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.99,Thinking,,0,0,0,,To beat Kaiou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.04,Memory,,0,0,0,,Why don't you play when you haunt the third guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! This pisses me off! What happened to him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki-san said the same thing the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a player he likes on a losing streak?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Another forfeit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsubaki-san, are you done eating? The\Ncompany president wants to play you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of my free time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? It's a chance for you to get some points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only does he suck, he hates losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is he good at Go or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear he took the pro exam last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a guy like that, maybe\NI should learn a bit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, it's all crumpled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that crumpled up newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Kawai-san do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawai-san, the newspapers are for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't crumple them just because\NShindou-kun has another forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what's wrong.\NWhy does he have forfeits?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to cheer him on like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he has his reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you be a little more patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you men!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Our patience set aside, can pros get\Nfired for not going to the matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Can they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fired!? You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I went all the way to Hiroshima with\Nhim! And spent a night there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:38.14,Background,,0,0,0,,Kawai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:45.19,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs16\1c&H54625F&\bord0\shad0\frz345\fscy120\move(426,495,352,210)}Japanese Go Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just barely managed to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:06.50,Background,,0,0,0,,Ochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging by the fact that you were in\Nthe bathroom, you must have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.85,Background,,0,0,0,,You have this habit of going to the\Nbathroom whenever you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a biological function.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.85,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm still continuing my winning\Nstreak, unlike you, Waya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya have you heard? The head of the pros\Ncommittee, Murota 9-dan called Shindou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked whether Shindou was sick,\Nor if he needed to file for a leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but he couldn't get a clear-cut answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's going to quit being a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And to think people thought\Nhe could be Touya's rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Genius is meaningless if you don't play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:13.94,Thinking,,0,0,0,,A tournament... what fond memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:19.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Mitani was first board, Tsutsui-san\Nwas second, and I was third...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I was the worst player back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We won against Iwata Jr. High in the first round 3-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.26,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I even remember what the guy I played looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:56.65,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:01.33,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.65,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou, going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nothing better to do\Nright? Can I ask for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean I have nothing better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you aren't going to any of the pro matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Play Mitani a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Play Mitani?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's working hard to prepare for the tournament,\Nbut there's no one he can practice with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.59,Background,,0,0,0,,Kaneko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business. I don't\Nwant a guy like him coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:16.15,Background,,0,0,0,,If Shindou can play you, then I'm\Nfree to teach Natsume or Koike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Kaneko-san. Mitani-kun. Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:41.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We're all working hard... that's what I thought. But\NI guess it can't be helped if Mitani's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The Go club will take care of it by\Nitself. Sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The tournament is next Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come watch at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.38,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Our dream of participating in the\Ntournament is coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't drag everyone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh it's over! That was just horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Akari, another game!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's so passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.87,0:14:49.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Hikaru was like this too when he was in the Go club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.79,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong with him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:58.50,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Did he forget what he was like back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the last tournament in Jr. High for us\Nthird year students, so let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's go, Kumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm going first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.25,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs11\1c&H6C1D26&\fad(626,0)\bord0\fscx100\fscy160\blur0\shad1\4c&HFFFFFF&\frz355\frx6\fry18\pos(523,332)}Kaiou Private Junior High School
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:41.42,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs11\1c&H6C1D26&\fad(0,0)\bord0\fscx100\fscy160\blur0\shad1\4c&HFFFFFF&\frz355\frx6\fry18\pos(523,332)}Kaiou Private J{\alpha&HFF&}unior High School
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It probably started already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.47,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I won't be playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:34.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:39.69,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'm only watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:51.07,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs15.5\an4\1c&H554A47&\bord0\blur2\fad(209,0)\fscy200\shad0\frz3.5\pos(400,172)}IGO TOURNA-\NMENT HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:59.46,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H2B4006&\bord1\shad0\alpha&H40&}The Sixth Annual Summer Go Tournament Match Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:16.64,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs11\1c&H414043&\3c&HE6F6F6&\bord4\fad(0,2669)\shad0\blur0\fscx99\fscy195\frz1\move(75,11,669,11,67,10369)}The Sixth Annual North District Summer Junior High Go Tournament
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:41.91,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's Akari!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.08,Thinking,,0,0,0,,She's sitting in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:47.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So she's second board...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What is she thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:06.44,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's an easy life and death problem. Don't\Npanic. Think carefully about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:12.07,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:19.12,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Mitani...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.86,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I can't want to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.90,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I were to want to play...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.45,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If I were to play Go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:26.08,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai... would be gone forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.17,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I know it...
